2.title: Funeral Casserole!

episode of.title: Lili & Eduard Present: Whipping Up Trouble! (TV Series 2015– )

2.plot: With a "show must go on" attitude, Lili dedicates her second episode to dearly departed Aunt Jan, choosing to highlight one of Jan's most famous recipes, "Funeral Casserole". Even though Jan may be departed, she may not have gone very far.

3.title: The Tasteful Telethon

episode of.title: Lili & Eduard Present: Whipping Up Trouble! (TV Series 2015– )

3.plot: Lili Fenstermeyer will stop at nothing to save her kitchen. After the death of her Aunt Jan, Lili must take over monthly rent of $2,000. With her web empire still under construction, Lili decides to host a telethon to raise money to keep "Whipping Up Trouble!" cooking. When the telethon fizzles, Lili decides to make one of her guiltiest pleasure recipes, "The Lonely Girl Dinner", with some wonderful results.

4.title: Chicken Saltimbocca

episode of.title: Lili & Eduard Present: Whipping Up Trouble! (TV Series 2015– )

4.plot: After episode 3 (The Lonely Girl Dinner) goes viral, Lili Fenstermeyer's career is cooking with 1000 FOLLOWERS. In the mid-season finale, Lili works out her aggression by pounding poultry and making Chicken Saltimbocca. When an unexpected visitor arrives to deliver news to Lili mid-broadcast, her world is turned upside down and the future of Lili and Eduard's web-show is put into jeopardy.
